# ==================================================
# üõ°Ô∏è SECURITY CHECKLIST - VERIFY BEFORE COMMITTING
# ==================================================

# ‚úÖ Run this command before every commit:
# git check-ignore -v --no-index YOUR_FILE_NAME

# ‚úÖ Always check:
# 1. No .keystore or .jks files
# 2. No local.properties
# 3. No google-services.json (if template project)
# 4. No .env files with secrets
# 5. No build folders

# ==================================================
# üéØ PRO TIPS FOR FLUTTER DEVELOPERS
# ==================================================

# 1. Use `flutter clean` before committing to remove build artifacts
# 2. Use `git status` to verify no sensitive files are staged
# 3. Use environment variables for API keys, never hardcode
# 4. Keep signing keys in secure location, never in repo
# 5. Use CI/CD for builds, never commit APK/AAB files

# ==================================================
# üîí FINAL SECURITY REMINDER
# ==================================================
# IF YOU COMMIT SENSITIVE FILES:
# 1. They are PERMANENT in git history
